仲未明 <br />\n靠人不如靠自己呢個道理<br />\n咁抵你死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賺到錢既野 唔係冇 <br />\n不過唔會俾你萬幾蚊玩到羅"},{"pid":"bbfb9e63d885732250748af0c10256a31534eb32","tid":1091143,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"啲騙徒點解要用馬會 唔用銀行<br />\n<br />\n用馬會要追蹤 一樣追蹤到"},{"pid":"d3c0aa6ffe6eed8bc5d694058c6519560d6a1890","tid":1091143,"uid":164928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"玩21點都可以輸凸就咪學人賭啦<br />\n<br />\n但用三萬想賺四十八萬都唔叫貪<br />\n唔通真係渣刀老笠先叫貪？"},{"pid":"4dd205fce17e52cc3d685fa07b5eaadb0afff648","tid":1091143,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:20:17.000Z","msg":"3萬本錢（1萬5千自己+1萬5千借朋友）博48萬分紅<br />\n<br />\n唔貪心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}